snippet.title: Warmonium™: Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Featuring team fighting turn based tactics with multilevel path finding. Inspired by late 90's to early 2000's board games it's a fantasy come true for fans of strategy war games! Catering to the casual and competitive player, from ranked games to custom maps.

Logic Leo unveils Warmonium: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvX9X49FhOw&ab_channel=LogicLeo

Play now on Steam!
www.warmonium.com.au

K
